# Force LF everywhere. The OTA updater verifies downloaded files against
# sha256 hashes in version.json — those are computed on LF bytes, and
# raw.githubusercontent.com serves the repo blob verbatim. Any CRLF conversion
# would cause every hash to mismatch and block updates. Keep it LF end to end.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
